<item>
            <title>[SPR-742] old version of  mysql driver bundled</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-742</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The hibernate version of the petclinic doesn&apos;t work on mysql because an obselete version of the mysql jdbc driver (2.0.14) is bundled, which results in the following exception when trying to insert records&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.AbstractMethodError: com.mysql.jdbc.jdbc2.Connection.prepareStatement&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Suggested fix: bundle the latest 3.0.x mysql jdbc driver (this fixes the issue for me).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="11200">SPR-742</key>
            <summary>old version of  mysql driver bundled</summary>
